WHITE RIVER &#8211; A man was attacked by three men in his home in the early hours of this morning.The incident occured on a farm in the Heidel Valley.According to Hi-Tech Security, the man woke up at around 04:00 to find the men standing next to his bed.They demanded money and weapons.A struggle ensued and the victim was cut on the head and stabbed in the arm.The men made off with cash and a cell phone. They escaped through a fence.Their spoor was tracked. Nobody has been arrested yet.